# Repository Standards

## Package Manager

- Use pnpm for all operations.
- Do not introduce npm or yarn.

## Structure

Monorepo layout:

- apps/web → Next.js application
- packages/* → shared modules
- docs/* → canonical documentation
- prisma/* → Prisma schema + migrations

Do not introduce new top-level directories without updating docs/DECISIONS.md.

## Scripts

Maintain root-level scripts for:

- pnpm dev
- pnpm lint
- pnpm format
- pnpm test
- pnpm typecheck

## Code Quality

- Strict TypeScript required.
- Lint must pass.
- Type errors are not allowed.
